-- ── Batch 5: May 2026 (19 rows, revenue = 2,710,000) ───────

-- ── Batch 6: June 2026 (24 rows, revenue = 3,770,000) ──────

-- ── Batch 7: July 2026 (26 rows, revenue = 4,300,000) ──────

-- ── Batch 8: August 2026 (24 rows, revenue = 4,050,000) ────

-- ── Batch 9: September 2026 (27 rows, revenue = 4,485,000) ─

